% ====================================================================
% bench_unify_match_long_leaves.trx
% ====================================================================
% Synthetic worst-case microbenchmark for Option B (context-aware
% lvar_bind) from plan_lvar_bind_context_aware.md.
%
% Tight loop: unify-match a value of 10 Long leaves against a pattern
% of 10 lvar leaves, repeated 100k times.  This is the maximal case
% for Option B's per-leaf clone cost -- every leaf is an ExtValue-
% bearing scalar, every leaf bind takes the deep-clone path.
%
% Pre-Option B (shallow share): each per-iter bind transferred 10 Long
% offsets into the lvar bindings (0 extra ExtValue allocs).
% Post-Option B (deep clone on recursion): each per-iter bind allocates
% 10 fresh ExtValues for the lvar bindings (+10 allocs).  100k iters
% = 1M extra alloc/free roundtrips.
%
% Per-roundtrip cost: ~50-200ns on the local-VM free-list path (LIFO
% pop is O(1)).  Expected total overhead: 50-200ms.
%
% Excluded from tests/run_all.sh by naming convention (bench_*).
% Run manually for A/B comparison:
%
%   /usr/bin/time -f "%e" ./trix.opt tests/bench_unify_match_long_leaves.trx
%
% Compare wall-time output for trix.pre-optionB.opt vs trix.post-optionB.opt.
% ====================================================================

% --- Set up the iter body.  Each call:
%       1. allocate 10 fresh lvars
%       2. allocate value array [42l..800l]
%       3. allocate pattern array [a..j]
%       4. unify-match value against [[pattern { }]]
%       5. restore the per-iter save scope
{
    save /S exch def
    logic-var /a exch def
    logic-var /b exch def
    logic-var /c exch def
    logic-var /d exch def
    logic-var /e exch def
    logic-var /f exch def
    logic-var /g exch def
    logic-var /h exch def
    logic-var /i exch def
    logic-var /j exch def
    [ 42l 99l 100l 200l 300l 400l 500l 600l 700l 800l ]
    [[ [ a b c d e f g h i j ] { } ]] unify-match
    S restore
} /iter exch def

% --- Tight loop.  100k iterations of the body above.
100000 /iter load repeat

(bench_unify_match_long_leaves: 100k iterations complete) =
(__test_ok__) =
